{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Krakow was very exciting, because people came back from Russia, from deep in Siberia-- everywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From every parts they were sent during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They realize the only place is to be in a big city so they will be safe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Krakow was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the only city that wasn't bombed during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a beautiful-- it was very historic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The kings of Poland once lived there, and the Wawel, which is the palace, is there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what's more interesting for the Jewish people, the Remuh Shul is still standing there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Remuh Shul is 5-- about somewhere like 500 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was built in the middle-- like 15 something hundreds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Many hundreds of years it's standing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's the oldest, most historic shul standing in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was living not far from there, so that I could walk around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember going to the Wawel and-- and experiencing this beautiful city after the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was a very great experience, because, you know, this is the most beautiful city in Poland, the most cultured before the war-- one of the most cultured city and the most beautiful.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were the parks, and I could walk in the parks, and I took pictures I have today, in the winter, in the summer and-- it was exciting.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was an excitement like no other city after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was glad that I could be in that city, not in my-- scared in my village where I could be killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, I felt safe and beautiful in the most gorgeous-- I realized it was the most-- anybody who was there realized that you are in the most beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
